<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 pt-16 pb-24">

  <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">Feeds power the open web — RSS, Atom, JSON Feed, AT Protocol — but the infrastructure around them has gaps. feedspec.org is where we publish open specifications to fill them.</p>

  <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">These specs extend existing feed formats, not replace them. They build on standards you already use and degrade gracefully — readers that don't support them just see what they always have.</p>

